org.jdesktop.swingx.painter

Class BusyPainter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdesktop.beans.AbstractBean
      • org.jdesktop.swingx.painter.AbstractPainter<Object>
        • org.jdesktop.swingx.painter.BusyPainter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Painter<Object>

    @JavaBean
public class BusyPainter
extends AbstractPainter<Object>
    A specific painter that paints an "infinite progress" like animation.
